Class SwingSheetViewDelegate

java.lang.Object
com.dua3.meja.ui.SheetViewDelegate
com.dua3.meja.ui.swing.SwingSheetViewDelegate
All Implemented Interfaces:
Flow.Subscriber<SheetEvent>
public class SwingSheetViewDelegate extends SheetViewDelegate
The SwingSheetViewDelegate class is responsible for managing the interaction and rendering logic for a SwingSheetView in the context of a given Sheet. It connects the sheet data model with the visual representation using rendering and painting mechanisms.

This class utilizes a CellRenderer to specify how individual cells in the sheet should be rendered, and a SheetPainter to manage the overall visual rendering of the entire sheet.

Inherits from SheetViewDelegate, providing specific functionality for Swing-based sheet views.
